Dear E*TRADE Customer:

Congratulations! You've taken your first step on the road to financial
freedom and opened an E*TRADE investment account.

Now it's time to take the next steps. Follow the instructions below to
access your Online Welcome Kit, where you can easily explore the wide
range of resources available to you as an E*TRADE customer.

1. Go to http://www.etrade.com/welcome
2. Click the yellow Get Started button.
3. Enter your pre-selected User Name and Password.
4. Click the Log On button.

We hope you enjoy and profit from your relationship with E*TRADE.
We look forward to serving your financial needs for many years to come.

Sincerely,

